OL,6,FChris was called out with other
OL,7,Fmembers of the Patterdale Mountain
OL,8,FRescue team to help two men, who were
OL,9,Flater fined for breaching Covid
OL,10,Flockdown rules after they travelled
OL,11,Ffrom Liverpool and Leicester.
OL,13,FThey were called out in the middle of
OL,14,Fa dark, cloudy night when it's
OL,15,Fbelieved Chris fell.
OL,17,FMatthew Cox, who had led the team that
OL,18,Fnight, described how he went looking
OL,19,Ffor Chris when he realised he had not
OL,20,Fmade it to the campers.
