OL,6,FHe went looking for him along the icy
OL,7,Ftrack when he found Chris' helmet and
OL,8,Fglasses, and and then below, Chris.
OL,10,FChris received immediate medical
OL,11,Fattention from his colleagues before
OL,12,Fbeing airlifted to hospital in Preston.
OL,14,FAfter a long period in intensive care
OL,15,FChris returned home, quadriplegic,
OL,16,Fneeding 24-hour care.
OL,18,FHundreds of thousands of pounds were
OL,19,Fraised to help support his recovery at
OL,20,Fhome.
